President Jiang is the CEO of the company now.

102
00:07:10,060 --> 00:07:12,620
She has the final say in the company affairs.

103
00:07:27,300 --> 00:07:29,720
Sorry to keep you waiting. Here's your coffee.

104
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,680
Please enjoy it.

105
