222
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:51,580
What?

223
00:15:55,860 --> 00:16:02,380

224
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:05,480
Xiao Jiang, the headquarters thought

225
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:08,700
