226
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:12,760
So we have to announce publicly

227
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:15,460
the suspension of Ji Chen's duty.

228
00:16:18,060 --> 00:16:23,660
We suggest that the announcement be made today,

229
00:16:23,660 --> 00:16:27,540
with the promise that we'll have a thorough investigation of the matter.

230
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:31,320
This is the announcement we have drawn up.

231
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:33,420
Please have a look.

232
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,220
If you are all right with it,

233
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:37,020
