236
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:52,760
But I have to add some items to the announcement

237
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:56,160
to make it more practical.

238
00:16:57,500 --> 00:17:01,600
We should publicize the latest investigation result.

239
00:17:01,600 --> 00:17:02,900
What result?

240
00:17:02,900 --> 00:17:05,980
The only connection between Xing Yi and Extreme Impala

241
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:08,920
