242
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,980
a film called Phantom City

243
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:14,000
to the investors as a financial product

244
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:16,080
in the name of Qiao Yi being the producer.

245
00:17:16,080 --> 00:17:19,540
This is the program description of the film.

246
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:22,660
The confirmation letter signed by Qiao Yi is included.

247
00:17:22,660 --> 00:17:24,580
Xing Yi is also on the list of their producers.

248
00:17:24,580 --> 00:17:27,320
However, I have confirmed that

249
00:17:27,320 --> 00:17:30,940
Xing Yi has never signed the contract with Qiao Yi,

250
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:36,400
nor any investment contract.

251
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:39,860
You should ask Ji Chen to explain.

252
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:42,000
He is Qiao Yi's talent manager.

253
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,320
He must have been in charge of the matter.

254
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:47,600
The document appeared in the group chat of Extreme Impala at the earliest

255
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,900
at the end of last year,

256
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:51,400
earlier than the time I took over Xing Yi.

257
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:56,680
So you mean

258
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,920
the document is fake?

259
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:00,660
No.

260
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:02,840
I have checked that

261
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:04,940
the official seal on the contract was true.

262
00:18:04,940 --> 00:18:06,560
It suggests that

263
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:09,240
it was made by someone inside Xing Yi.

264
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:11,660
Qiao Yi's talent manager back then was Lucy.

265
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:12,940
And he said that

266
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:16,860
Lucy asked him to attend Extreme Impala's party.

267
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:23,720
