270
00:18:27,080 --> 00:18:29,900
She turned off her phone, and her whereabouts remain unknown.

271
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:32,380
So? What's the point of your proof?

272
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:33,700
It didn't make any difference.

273
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:35,680
Though her whereabouts still remain unknown,

274
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:40,800
I have found the producer on the paper.

275
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:44,120
I got his recordings.

276
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:48,720
Producer?

277
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:57,120
Please, we all are pretty busy.

278
00:18:57,120 --> 00:18:59,500
We don't have much time to watch your show.

279
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:02,100
If you do have the proof, show it to us.

280
00:19:06,940 --> 00:19:09,400
Uncle Chen is right.

281
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:16,960
 Can you explain the whole thing to us?

282
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:19,140
 The project doesn't exist at all.

283
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:24,480
 Extreme Impala asked me to make a film for them.

284
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:28,340
 They said Qiao Yi would be the scriptwriter, and wished that I could do the budget.

285
00:19:28,340 --> 00:19:31,060
 I was afraid it was a trap,

286
00:19:31,060 --> 00:19:35,340
 so I asked to have a face-to-face negotiation with Qiao Yi's talent manager.

287
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:37,860
 They showed me a confirmation letter with Qiao Yi's signature.

288
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:38,860

289
00:19:38,860 --> 00:19:40,260
 I wasn't completely convinced,

290
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:41,580
 with the fear that it could be a fake one.

291
00:19:41,580 --> 00:19:45,260
 So I asked my friend to contact Lucy.

292
00:19:45,260 --> 00:19:48,700
 Lucy confirmed it with me in person.

293
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:50,260
 We had the meeting a few times,

294
00:19:50,260 --> 00:19:52,220
 and started to talk with actors and actresses.

295
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,900
 They then said it wasn't urgent.

296
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:57,000
 They needed a program description from me.

297
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,920
 I wasn't secure then,

298
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:01,260
 so I told them we should first put it on record in the National Film Board.

299
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:04,000
 I need them to offer the letter of investment confirmation.

300
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,500
 I heard them make a phone call to a man,

301
00:20:07,500 --> 00:20:09,940
 who was President Chen from Xing Yi.

302
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:14,140
 That President Chen said he would deliver the letter with the seal to us.

303
00:20:14,140 --> 00:20:16,280
 Have you met President Chen?

304
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:19,460
 After the meeting that night, they had dinner together.

305
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:21,200
 I wasn't invited.

306
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:23,080
 But I saw President Chen come.

307
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:24,980
 I gave them the stamped document.

308
00:20:24,980 --> 00:20:26,620
 And they copied one and sent it to me.

309
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:28,500
 Then, they went for dinner.

310
00:20:28,500 --> 00:20:31,460
 Later, I realized that this project was entirely infeasible.

311
00:20:31,460 --> 00:20:33,960
 They promised to sign the contract but didn't.

312
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:36,980
 So, I dropped the project.

313
00:20:40,120 --> 00:20:44,220
President Chen. Please explain yourself.

314
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:56,740
What do you mean?

315
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,540
Just because of this recording?

316
00:20:58,540 --> 00:21:02,500
Are you implying that I'm the guy he mentioned?

317
00:21:04,780 --> 00:21:07,960
First, I'm not even sure whether this sound recording is authentic.

318
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:11,260
Besides, how did he know

319
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:17,280
that President Chen was the actual president of Xing Yi?

320
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:20,200
As far as I can see it, you arranged this person.

321
00:21:21,220 --> 00:21:24,500
Well, we can get him up here and let him speak.

322
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:27,180
He's waiting in the car downstairs.

323
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:29,360
You have two options now.

324
00:21:29,360 --> 00:21:32,340
We can let the police have him, and they will take over the matter.

325
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:36,540
Or you tell everyone here what happened.

326
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:41,780
Uncle Chen. Don't be nervous.

327
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:43,840
My father and you have been good friends for so long.

328
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:46,700
Last night, I told him about you.

329
00:21:46,700 --> 00:21:51,920
He thought that as long as you admit and turn in the money,

330
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:54,680
we will handle this ourselves.

331
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:57,420
Otherwise, we will call the police.

332
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:04,200

(T/N: 110 is the equivalent to U.S. 911)

333
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:06,640
You have 10 seconds.

334
00:22:07,180 --> 00:22:10,080
One, two...

335
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:12,160
Seven...

336
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:15,560
What? That's way too fast.

337
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:16,840
Nine...

338
00:22:16,840 --> 00:22:18,560
Fine.

339
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:29,280
I'll admit it.

340
00:22:30,620 --> 00:22:35,120
Back then, Extreme Impala reached me.

341
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:39,300
They said they could turn film and television projects into financial products.

342
00:22:39,900 --> 00:22:43,740
And I could get the money back before shooting.

343
00:22:43,740 --> 00:22:46,800
I had no idea the company could collapse.

344
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:54,240
Later, they asked me to get Screenwriter Confirmation Letter
from Qiao Yi.

345
00:22:54,960 --> 00:22:57,440
I asked Lucy to get it.

346
00:23:02,020 --> 00:23:04,000
How about this?

347
00:23:05,120 --> 00:23:09,040
I'll turn in every penny I received.

348
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:12,090
You all can act like you don't know about this.

349
00:23:14,100 --> 00:23:18,540
We can, but the police won't allow it.

350
00:23:18,540 --> 00:23:21,120
We should let the police handle this.

351
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:22,780
Hold on.

352
00:23:24,380 --> 00:23:30,940
Xiao Jiang. You just said you wouldn't call the police.

353
00:23:32,540 --> 00:23:33,940
What did I just say?

354
00:23:33,940 --> 00:23:36,440
You said we would handle it ourselves, instead of calling the police.

355
00:23:38,300 --> 00:23:40,100
My dad suggested we keep it from the police.

356
00:23:40,100 --> 00:23:42,900
But that doesn't mean he won't call the police.

357
00:23:42,900 --> 00:23:44,460
You...

358
00:23:47,140 --> 00:23:48,820
President Chen.

359
00:23:49,420 --> 00:23:51,320
What a hero you are.

360
00:23:51,320 --> 00:23:53,320
I'm not a hero.

361
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:55,280
I just don't want you, a taekwondo pro,

362
00:23:55,280 --> 00:23:58,280
to break his ribs if he actually goes near you.

363
00:23:58,280 --> 00:24:00,940
In that case, we can't explain ourselves to the police.

364
00:24:00,940 --> 00:24:02,780
You are right.

365
00:24:02,780 --> 00:24:04,960
Smart.

366
00:24:04,960 --> 00:24:06,800
Good move.

367
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:09,840

368
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,400
 Today, the police uncovered a consumer-related case

369
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:13,300
 of Extreme Impala company bankruptcy.

370
00:24:13,300 --> 00:24:15,000
 They have arrested all the relevant personnel,

371
00:24:15,000 --> 00:24:17,180
 including two Xing Yi employees.

372
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:20,520
 Jiang Hanyi, the president of Xing Yi Media, also made a special statement.

373
00:24:20,520 --> 00:24:24,800
 First of all, I would like to offer my deep apology

374
00:24:24,800 --> 00:24:27,000
 to all victims of this incident.

375
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:36,460
 Although this incident has nothing to do with Xing Yi,

376
00:24:36,460 --> 00:24:40,460
 we do have to do better at supervising our employees.

377
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:42,800
 We are partly responsible.

378
00:24:42,800 --> 00:24:45,680
President Chen just got arrested, and President Jiang was already making the statement.

379
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,400
It's clearly planned in advance.

380
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:50,060
Zhou Tian, you discovered the project proposal.

381
00:24:50,060 --> 00:24:52,060
How could President Ji not tell you about this?

382
00:24:52,060 --> 00:24:55,680
It's pretty obvious. President Ji and President Jiang didn't want her to know in the first place.

383
00:24:57,340 --> 00:25:01,020
I guess I'm not qualified to know.

384
00:25:01,020 --> 00:25:02,680
Zhou Tian,

385
00:25:05,660 --> 00:25:07,780
you came to me that day?

386
00:25:09,580 --> 00:25:12,960
I heard that the producer of the project happened to be filming in the mountains,

387
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:14,420
so I rushed over there overnight.

388
00:25:14,420 --> 00:25:17,140
When I got there, my cell phone had no signal.

389
00:25:17,140 --> 00:25:18,740
After recording, my phone was dead.

390
00:25:18,740 --> 00:25:21,260
I didn't even get a chance to tell you.

391
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:24,740
Sorry. Don't be angry with me. I didn't mean to keep it from you.

392
00:25:24,740 --> 00:25:27,080
- He's apologizing. 
 - He's apologizing.

393
00:25:28,280 --> 00:25:31,340
It's all right, President Ji. You don't have to explain to me.

394
00:25:31,340 --> 00:25:33,640
I do.

395
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:38,220
You being upset is more serious to me than the board of directors and other people.

396
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,760
Dominating.

397
00:25:39,760 --> 00:25:40,880
So sweet.

398
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:42,860
Too sweet.

399
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:48,220
Zhou Tian, I knew you were worried about me.

400
00:25:48,220 --> 00:25:51,860
If it weren't for you, I wouldn't have found that proposal.

401
00:25:54,780 --> 00:25:57,700
Now, let's forget about that.

402
00:25:57,700 --> 00:26:00,380
We can get some food later.

403
00:26:00,380 --> 00:26:02,240
What do you want to have?

404
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:09,580
Guys, you are in the office now. Behave.

405
00:26:09,580 --> 00:26:12,180
I invited shareholders for lunch. You come with me.

406
00:26:12,180 --> 00:26:14,940
When did you invite them? Just now.

407
00:26:18,360 --> 00:26:20,860
This is going to be a good show.

408
00:26:23,060 --> 00:26:27,620
♪ It was raining that day when you held me ♪

409
00:26:27,620 --> 00:26:31,400
♪ A shooting star fell in my heart secretly ♪

410
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:33,700
♪ It found a place in your eyes ♪

411
00:26:33,700 --> 00:26:36,100
♪ and witnessed my promise to you ♪

412
00:26:36,100 --> 00:26:41,230
♪ Eventually, it brightened my whole universe ♪

413
00:26:53,360 --> 00:26:55,380
Hi, Zhou Tian.

414
00:26:55,380 --> 00:26:59,100
Zhou Tian. This is the news release for Qiao Yi's book launch.

415
00:26:59,100 --> 00:27:00,660
How is the rehearsal?

416
00:27:00,660 --> 00:27:04,420
It went well. I went there this afternoon. Both of them were in good condition.

417
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:07,620
We tested everything, including the sound, light, and screen.

418
00:27:07,620 --> 00:27:09,220
They will have the last joint rehearsal tonight.

419
00:27:09,220 --> 00:27:11,120
I'll go check again later today.

420
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,540
All right.

421
00:27:14,980 --> 00:27:17,240
President Ji is not back yet?

422
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:20,500
No. Neither President Jiang nor he has come back.

423
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:24,000
Aren't they going to watch the joint rehearsal?

424
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:29,980
I'll get going then.

425
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:34,380

426
00:27:38,640 --> 00:27:40,500
President Jiang.

427
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:44,620
Go to Ji Chen's place?

428
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,320

429
00:28:01,700 --> 00:28:04,980
Ji Chen is not at home. Take a seat.

430
00:28:13,980 --> 00:28:17,540
President Jiang. What do you want?

431
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:21,480
The concert is about to begin tomorrow. I'm quite busy.

432
00:28:36,640 --> 00:28:39,080
As long as you leave Ji Chen,

433
00:28:39,080 --> 00:28:42,080
I can give you the position of department director.

434
00:28:46,820 --> 00:28:49,760
Ji Chen is not a commodity with negotiated price.

435
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:52,720
You don't deserve to like him at all.

436
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:56,640
I don't? Do you?

437
00:28:56,640 --> 00:29:00,580
Zhou Tian, you're letting Ji Chen dangle.

438
00:29:00,580 --> 00:29:05,980
Playing hard to get is too childish.

439
00:29:08,100 --> 00:29:09,960
If you keep pestering him,

440
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:13,220
I'll make him unable to take the CEO position back forever.

441
00:29:16,100 --> 00:29:18,520
Is this how you get the person you like?

442
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:21,420
You are threatening him with his career, one thing that he cares about the most.

443
00:29:22,500 --> 00:29:26,260
No wonder he didn't go to watch the rehearsal of Qiao Yi and Li Ang.

444
00:29:27,060 --> 00:29:29,920
I just want him to see the bigger picture here.

445
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:32,420
Tell me. What do you want?

446
00:29:32,420 --> 00:29:36,360
I can give you anything as long as you name it.

447
00:29:37,140 --> 00:29:39,740
What do I want?

448
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:44,420
There are certain things in this world that you can't buy with money.

449
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:48,380
At least, you can't buy my affection to Ji Chen.

450
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:53,200
President Jiang. You don't have to threaten me with his career.

451
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:55,720
No matter what happens, I'll face it with him.

452
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,820
I like him, and he likes me.

453
00:29:57,820 --> 00:30:00,840
Nothing and nobody can break us apart.

454
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:05,580
What a confession of love.

455
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:12,020
Ji Chen. Did you hear that?

456
00:30:12,020 --> 00:30:13,760
You...

457
00:30:16,300 --> 00:30:20,020

458
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:24,900
Now, I declare,

459
00:30:24,900 --> 00:30:30,260
I'm done being the bad guy here.

460
00:30:30,260 --> 00:30:32,280
W-What does that mean?

461
00:30:32,280 --> 00:30:35,840
Please don't be mad.

462
00:30:35,840 --> 00:30:37,320
The reason why I'm back this time

463
00:30:37,320 --> 00:30:39,880
 was to help Ji Chen to pursue you.

464
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:41,820
 He may seem to be vigorous and resolute.

465
00:30:41,820 --> 00:30:44,900
He has never been in a relationship before. He doesn't know about girls.

466
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:48,520
That's why I wanted to help him.

467
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,760
 Take a bite yourself.

468
00:31:06,260 --> 00:31:08,880
 You want me to help you with dressing?

469
00:31:13,520 --> 00:31:15,900
So, you were targeting me all along?

470
00:31:15,900 --> 00:31:18,480
And you pretended to sacrifice Ji Chen?

471
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,680
All was but a scam?

472
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:25,240
It wasn't all a scam.

473
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:29,520
We had to stabilize President Chen, you know?

474
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:33,580
Nevertheless, what do you think of our acting skills?

475
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,480
Good.

476
00:31:35,480 --> 00:31:36,800
Great.

477
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:39,900
So, Ji Chen knew everything?

478
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:43,000
You two planned all these from the very beginning, didn't you?

479
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:45,320
Yes, he knew. He liked the plan.

480
00:31:45,320 --> 00:31:46,720
I...

481
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:50,860
Zhou Tian, please listen to me.

482
00:31:50,860 --> 00:31:53,920
Jiang Hanyi, stop talking!

483
00:31:53,920 --> 00:31:56,960
Well... She's gone.

484
00:31:56,960 --> 00:31:58,880
And she seemed mad.

485
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:01,160
 But now, you have the chance to make her feel better.

486
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,480
Make yourself disappear now!

487
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:05,760
What's with the attitude?

488
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:07,900
I did make her confess her love to you.

489
00:32:07,900 --> 00:32:10,540
 I should at least get some credit for that. Don't you think so?

490
00:32:10,540 --> 00:32:13,460
 But I'm done playing here.

491
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:15,920
You have to take over from here.

492
00:32:15,920 --> 00:32:18,560
You can be the CEO again. Bye.

493
00:32:26,900 --> 00:32:28,740
Perfect.

494
00:32:32,480 --> 00:32:35,880
Hello? The car is here?

495
00:32:35,880 --> 00:32:37,580
Thanks.

496
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:51,180

497
00:33:04,940 --> 00:33:06,860
Thanks.

498
00:33:14,340 --> 00:33:18,900
Sweetie, I have successfully messed up Ji Chen's relationship.

499
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:23,680
Now, I can get out of here. See you in 12 hours.

500
00:33:26,540 --> 00:33:28,440
 I'll pick you up.

501
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:38,700
Thanks.

502
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:50,920
And we also arranged first-aid personnel and security guards.

503
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,660
Good. Security guards are already in place.

504
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:54,500
 Okay.

505
00:33:55,740 --> 00:33:57,420
Zhou Tian, can I have a word with you?

506
00:33:57,420 --> 00:33:58,500
Is it about work?

507
00:33:58,500 --> 00:34:00,240
I didn't lie to you. It was all Jiang Hanyi's doing...

508
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:03,180
President Ji. Li Ang's concert is about to begin.

509
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:05,180
And we have a lot to do here.

510
00:34:05,180 --> 00:34:08,360
Are you really gonna make me stand here and listen to your personal matters?

511
00:34:08,360 --> 00:34:11,920
This is very important. If we can't sort this out, we might as well stop the concert.

512
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:14,080
What?

513
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:17,480
This concert may mean nothing to you, but it means everything
to Li Ang and me.

514
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:19,400
Zhou Tian, he deceived you.

515
00:34:19,400 --> 00:34:23,100
You can't forgive him. Otherwise, I'll fire you.

516
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:29,040
You need me now? Hello? Yes, I heard you.

517
00:34:29,040 --> 00:34:32,280
Hey, Zhou Tian. Please listen to me.

518
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,400
- No, this matter—  
 - Attention, everyone.

519
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:34,820
There are five minutes left before the concert.

520
00:34:34,820 --> 00:34:36,140
The concert will be on in five minutes.

521
00:34:36,140 --> 00:34:37,860
I can think of nothing but work right now.

522
00:34:37,860 --> 00:34:40,960
Sorry. I really can't talk about your personal matters.

523
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,680
Wait, Zhou Tian.

524
00:34:44,060 --> 00:34:46,580
How can I explain myself to her?

525
00:34:46,580 --> 00:34:47,940
By the way, Boss.

526
00:34:47,940 --> 00:34:50,680
I think you do have feelings for Gigi.

527
00:34:50,680 --> 00:34:52,580
Why don't you tell her?

528
00:34:52,580 --> 00:34:55,340
It's not that I don't want to tell her.

529
00:34:55,340 --> 00:34:58,600
I just fear that it may be a misunderstanding.

530
00:34:58,600 --> 00:35:00,600
What do you mean?

531
00:35:01,940 --> 00:35:06,380
I'm not sure if she likes me for being me or being the champion.

532
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:10,120
